<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦来参加侄子的生日派对了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19777</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有个男人正在表演。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19778</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我叫查克。” 男人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在摆弄膝盖上的巨型玩偶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29796</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它叫查克斯。说‘你好’，查克斯。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29797</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35560</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好，查克斯！” 查克假装查克斯在说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35561</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是叔叔的嘴巴在动！” 一个小女孩儿说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39926</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“表演得太差劲了。” 一个小男孩儿说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>查克继续假装查克斯说：“查克，你不擅长这个！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52290</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“查克斯，这么说可不好！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52291</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58490</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是，我不好！我很坏，很坏，很坏！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62991</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探抱怨说：“ 表演得真是太差劲了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道要给蒂娜买什么。” 玛拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西和朋友们在 “都会玩具店” 。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那是美罗城最大的一家玩具店。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78356</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉要给表妹买一个礼物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78357</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81001</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“蒂娜几岁了？” 罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“两岁。” 玛拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89691</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，” 特勒尔说，“两岁的孩子喜欢什么呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克拿起一把塑料剑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“蒂娜会喜欢剑吗？” 杰克挥舞着剑说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99582</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他假装要打特勒尔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102892</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔笑着也拿起了剑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102893</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嘭！哐！特勒尔和杰克的剑碰到了一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110933</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西和玛拉翻了个白眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110934</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“蒂娜很有意思，” 玛拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116138</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我喜欢跟她玩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116139</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过，我不知道我不在的时候，她都做些什么。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124895</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“美术套盒怎么样？” 罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124896</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拿起一个套盒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“铅笔、毛笔、水彩涂料都有。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133109</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134993</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个容易脏。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134994</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>上次她来我家的时候，把番茄酱涂了一桌子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不能给她买水彩涂料。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149356</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这家店卖乐器，” 罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149357</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153343</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你可以给蒂娜买竖笛或者鼓。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153344</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉哼了一声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不行！蒂娜已经够吵了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164494</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！” 特勒尔后退时撞到了罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164495</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169006</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起，” 特勒尔说，“是杰克撞了我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169007</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克的剑挥过来，特勒尔挡住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177049</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西哈哈大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177050</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181559</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“特勒尔，真可惜火箭女孩儿不在这里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181560</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么？” 特勒尔问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西微笑着说：“她可以帮你打赢杰克！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190841</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不可能！” 杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190842</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193673</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就是火箭女孩儿也赢不了我。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193674</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196962</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我就是这个国家最勇敢的骑士！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196963</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈！” 特勒尔举起剑向杰克扑了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西拿起一把剑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206781</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，她的手表响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她悄悄地离开了朋友们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布洛姆市长？” 罗西说，“有什么事吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221621</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿，” 布洛姆市长说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221622</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225561</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我需要你去一下美罗城会展中心，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个周末那里有个大型玩偶展会。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233841</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有人偷走了一批非常珍贵的玩偶。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233842</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236931</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心，市长。” 罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236932</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿马上就去！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>